org.openscience.cdk.smsd.algorithm.rgraph

Class CDKRMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.smsd.algorithm.rgraph.CDKRMap

  • @TestClass(value="org.openscience.cdk.smsd.algorithm.cdk.CDKRMapTest")
public class CDKRMap
extends Object
    An CDKRMap implements the association between an edge (bond) in G1 and an edge (bond) in G2, G1 and G2 being the compared graphs in a RGraph context.
